{"tid":305934,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］係大阪唔見左passport","createTime":"2017-07-02T06:29:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T08:23:39.000Z","uid":22929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc048dd873ca4d68d21a93175553144a886bba92","tid":305934,"uid":22929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"今日摷個袋發現唔見左本passport 我最後一次拎過出黎係琴日難波玩具反斗城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家返緊去個邊諗住問有無執到 無既應該等陣去警署報失先<br />\n我聽晚就飛返香港 我想問下依家我有咩手續要做先出得境 個人好慌又唔知應該做d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b1e41dbd8ff767b91b72ed2e17dc367a3710a13","tid":305934,"uid":37,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:36:42.000Z","msg":"特衰既打1868去入境處同佢講聲唔見左passport先<br />\n跟住佢就會sd你啲資料去中國領事館<br />\n再打去領事館約個時間整快證<br />\n最緊要係去警察局報埋失<br />\n我嗰陣朝早發現唔見 晏就4點零就攞到快證<br />\n埋單7000羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c2ba6ca9b4458cbcb8824c4cf13c70d2dda020","tid":305934,"uid":37,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:40:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>特衰既打1868去入境處同佢講聲唔見左passport先<br />\n跟住佢就會sd你啲資料去中國領事館<br />\n再打去領事館約個時間整快證<br />\n最緊要係去警察局報埋失<br />\n我嗰陣朝早發現唔見 晏就4點零就攞到快證<br />\n埋單7000羊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過星期日領事館好似唔開<br />\n所以最好第二朝早啲過去<br />\n多數即日搞掂"},{"pid":"991e0828b80eb8678af95329d5ab0193cdf74130","tid":305934,"uid":37,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:43:23.000Z","msg":"領事館緊急電話：090-6673-6659"},{"pid":"0b0a5e51038aef29397ef6908a731f44aed0beca","tid":305934,"uid":135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:44:49.000Z","msg":"身份證有冇唔見？冇左身份證要等幾日，身份證仲係度既話比多D錢即日拎得"},{"pid":"6334cd5f2c0717a59668713405bc20cd5c2b295c","tid":305934,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去日本都唔見得咁唔小心"},{"pid":"98f33d810c67d955ce3319690e445ac15b4a6f3f","tid":305934,"uid":135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"領事館未開就好去排隊喇<br />\n我上次係東京中國領事館勁撚多中國人整唔知乜尻證<br />\n差D冇得整<br />\n<br />\n返到香港即刻續左本BNO，廁板續都廢事"},{"pid":"ac5385b99bc9aa7b6e84d2f253ec1ad928387025","tid":305934,"uid":22929,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我岩岩係難波park拎返了 應該有人執到 算係不幸中既大幸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次真係俾個教訓自己要keep好本passport"},{"pid":"2605506f4cd614a53873925ed1cbb1708b4d90ea","tid":305934,"uid":53798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T06:58:19.000Z","msg":"習慣會帶多份影印本，有無用"},{"pid":"0e52550f41893304c6ce8dd103937aff7bc528a7","tid":305934,"uid":25679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T08:23:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>習慣會帶多份影印本，有無用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該無...起碼出唔到境先"}]}